---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Home" description="Our mission is to support any person, family, friend or agency in Minnesota affected by hoarding through education, networking and resources.">

  <section class="hero">
    <img
      src="/images/2026-Membership-Drive-1.png"
      alt="2026 Membership Drive — Join the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force"
      class="hero-img"
      width="1439"
      height="809"
    />
  </section>

  <section class="intro section">
    <div class="container">
      <p>We are an all volunteer group of individuals and professionals who work in various fields or have a personal interest in hoarding. The Minnesota Hoarding Task Force educates the public and families about what hoarding is and is not. We respond to requests for help with hoarding situations and participate in community events with information for those affected by or who want to learn more about hoarding.</p>
      <p>We do not offer services, instead we use our expertise and connections to share information and options to be considered. <a href="/directory/">View our Resource Directory below.</a></p>
      <p>If you have a question about a hoarding situation, <a href="/contact/">contact us</a> by phone, email, or on our <a href="https://www.facebook.com/mnhtf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Facebook Page</a>. We always keep details of such situations confidential.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="full-width-image-section">
    <img
      src="/images/Screenshot-2024-12-10.png"
      alt="Minnesota Hoarding Task Force resources"
      class="full-width-img"
      width="1194"
      height="291"
    />
  </section>

  <section class="mission section bg-light">
    <div class="container mission-inner">
      <div class="mission-text">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to support any person, family, friend or agency in Minnesota affected by hoarding through education, networking and connection to resources while promoting public health and safety.</p>
        <img
          src="/images/AdobeStock_782317916.jpeg"
          alt="Community support for hoarding disorder"
          class="mission-photo"
          width="768"
          height="430"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="full-width-image-section">
    <img
      src="/images/Screenshot-2025-02-16.png"
      alt="MNHTF education and community events"
      class="full-width-img"
      width="1439"
      height="513"
    />
  </section>

  <section class="mission-detail section">
    <div class="container mission-detail-inner">
      <img
        src="/images/0V7A6098.jpg"
        alt="Minnesota Hoarding Task Force meeting"
        class="mission-side-photo"
        width="1024"
        height="871"
      />
      <div class="mission-detail-text">
        <p>We welcome opportunities throughout Minnesota to share information about hoarding behaviors and hoarding disorder. As a mental illness, hoarding has been misunderstood and stigmatized for far too long.</p>
        <p>We welcome others to join us at our Monthly Education and Business Meetings, where we network, learn from each other, and move forward on our mission to support all in Minnesota who are affected by hoarding. Meetings are held at rotating locations in the Metro area, and are open to the public. To attend in person or virtually, you can request an invitation by emailing us at <a href="mailto:info@mnhtf.org">info@mnhtf.org</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="full-width-image-section">
    <a href="/events-and-calendar/">
      <img
        src="/images/Events-click-here.png"
        alt="Click here for MNHTF events and calendar"
        class="full-width-img"
        width="1440"
        height="407"
      />
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="directory-cta section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Resource Directory</h2>
      <p>We are building an extensive Resource Directory in order to share lists of existing community services. We are working to include more categories and more situations for which help already exists.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="full-width-image-section">
    <a href="/directory/">
      <img
        src="/images/Directory-of-Resources.png"
        alt="Click here for Directory of Resources"
        class="full-width-img"
        width="1140"
        height="407"
      />
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="directory-cards section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-grid">
        <a href="/for-people-who-hoard/" class="cta-card">
          <h3>I am struggling with Hoarding Disorder&hellip;</h3>
          <p>Find resources and support for individuals living with hoarding disorder.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/for-friends-and-family/" class="cta-card">
          <h3>I am a friend or family member&hellip;</h3>
          <p>Learn how to support a loved one affected by hoarding.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/for-municipalities/" class="cta-card">
          <h3>I am a Municipality&hellip;</h3>
          <p>Resources for local government and code enforcement.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/for-property-managers/" class="cta-card">
          <h3>I am a Property Manager&hellip;</h3>
          <p>Tools and guidance for property managers dealing with hoarding situations.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="cta-center"><a href="/directory/" class="btn btn-primary">View Full Directory</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="email-signup-section">
    <div class="email-signup-inner">
      <div class="email-signup-card">
        <div class="email-signup-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
            <path d="M1.5 8.67v8.58a3 3 0 003 3h15a3 3 0 003-3V8.67l-8.928 5.493a3 3 0 01-3.144 0L1.5 8.67z"/>
            <path d="M22.5 6.908V6.75a3 3 0 00-3-3h-15a3 3 0 00-3 3v.158l9.714 5.978a1.5 1.5 0 001.572 0L22.5 6.908z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2>Join the Email List</h2>
        <p>News, invites to our Public Education &amp; Business Meetings, and more — right to your inbox.</p>
        <form
          class="email-signup-form"
          action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/mnhtf"
          method="post"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="embed" value="1" />
          <div class="email-signup-row">
            <input
              class="email-signup-input"
              type="email"
              name="email"
              required
              placeholder="Your email address"
              aria-label="Email address"
            />
            <button class="email-signup-btn" type="submit">Subscribe</button>
          </div>
          <p class="email-signup-privacy">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="facebook-section">
    <div class="facebook-inner">
      <div class="facebook-embed">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/page.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmnhtf&tabs=timeline&height=520&small_header=false&adapt_container_width=true&hide_cover=false&show_facepile=true&hide_cta=false"
          width="100%"
          height="520"
          style="border:none;overflow:hidden;"
          scrolling="no"
          frameborder="0"
          allowfullscreen={true}
          allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          title="MNHTF Facebook Page"
          loading="lazy"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="facebook-cta">
        <svg class="facebook-wordmark" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/>
        </svg>
        <h2>Stay Connected</h2>
        <p>Follow the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force on Facebook for news, upcoming events, community resources, and more.</p>
        <ul class="facebook-features" aria-label="What you'll find on our Facebook page">
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Event announcements &amp; reminders
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Hoarding awareness &amp; education
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Community resources &amp; support
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Task force updates &amp; news
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="https://www.facebook.com/mnhtf"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="facebook-follow-btn"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/></svg>
          Follow on Facebook
        </a>
        <p class="facebook-follower-count">Join 647+ followers in our community</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="full-width-image-section">
    <img
      src="/images/Screenshot-2024-07-21.png"
      alt="MNHTF community programs"
      class="full-width-img"
      width="1440"
      height="528"
    />
  </section>

  <section class="vision section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>We envision communities that implement best practices to support those affected by hoarding where individuals are supported with sustainable options while being treated with dignity and respect.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.hero {
  background: var(--color-bg-light);
  line-height: 0;
}
.hero-img {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}
.full-width-image-section {
  line-height: 0;
}
.full-width-img {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}
.bg-light {
  background-color: var(--color-bg-light);
}
.mission-inner {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-6);
}
.mission-photo {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 740px;
  height: auto;
  margin-top: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: 4px;
}
.mission-detail-inner {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-8);
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.mission-side-photo {
  width: 550px;
  max-width: 50%;
  height: auto;
  border-radius: 4px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.mission-detail-text {
  flex: 1;
}
.cta-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
  margin: var(--space-6) 0;
}
.cta-card {
  display: block;
  background: var(--color-white);
  border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: var(--space-6);
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--color-text);
  transition: border-color var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
}
.cta-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(4, 12, 222, 0.1);
  color: var(--color-text);
}
.cta-card h3 {
  font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}
.cta-card p {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
}
.cta-center {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: var(--space-6);
}
.email-signup-section {
  width: 100%;
  background-image: url('/images/Email-Background.png');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-4);
}
.email-signup-inner {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
.email-signup-card {
  background: var(--color-white);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-8);
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 560px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
  text-align: center;
}
.email-signup-icon {
  width: 56px;
  height: 56px;
  background: var(--color-primary);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 auto var(--space-4);
}
.email-signup-icon svg {
  width: 26px;
  height: 26px;
}
.email-signup-card h2 {
  color: var(--color-text-dark);
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
}
.email-signup-card > p {
  margin: 0 0 var(--space-6);
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  color: var(--color-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.email-signup-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-3);
}
.email-signup-input {
  flex: 1 1 0;
  min-width: 0;
  padding: 12px var(--space-4);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  font-family: var(--font-family);
  color: var(--color-text);
  background: var(--color-white);
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color var(--transition);
}
.email-signup-input:focus {
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
}
.email-signup-btn {
  padding: 12px var(--space-6);
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  font-family: var(--font-family);
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  white-space: nowrap;
  transition: background var(--transition);
}
.email-signup-btn:hover {
  background: var(--color-primary-dark);
}
.email-signup-privacy {
  margin: var(--space-3) 0 0;
  font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  color: var(--color-secondary);
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .email-signup-card {
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-6);
  }
  .email-signup-row {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .email-signup-btn {
    width: 100%;
  }
}

.facebook-section {
  background: var(--color-bg-light);
  padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-8);
}
.facebook-inner {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-6);
  max-width: var(--max-width);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: var(--space-6);
  background: var(--color-white);
  border-radius: 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}
.facebook-embed {
  flex: 1 1 0;
  min-width: 0;
  max-width: 500px;
}
.facebook-embed iframe {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 8px;
}
.facebook-cta {
  flex: 1 1 340px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-5);
  color: #fff;
  background: var(--color-primary);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: var(--space-8);
}
.facebook-wordmark {
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  fill: #fff;
}
.facebook-cta h2 {
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.25;
}
.facebook-cta > p {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  line-height: 1.65;
}
.facebook-features {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-3);
}
.facebook-features li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-3);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.facebook-features li svg {
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
}
.facebook-follow-btn {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: var(--space-2);
  background: #fff;
  color: #040CDE;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1rem;
  padding: 14px var(--space-6);
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
  margin-top: var(--space-2);
}
.facebook-follow-btn svg {
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  fill: #040CDE;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  transition: fill 0.15s ease;
}
.facebook-follow-btn:hover {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
}
.facebook-follower-count {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  margin: 0;
  text-align: center;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .facebook-inner {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }
  .facebook-embed {
    width: 100%;
  }
  .facebook-cta {
    flex: none;
    width: 100%;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .mission-detail-inner {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .mission-side-photo {
    max-width: 100%;
    width: 100%;
  }
}
</style>
